    Seeking an intern who can observe behavior of potential users and improve design of existing Ruby on Rails site. This is your opportunity to work and learn alongside a developers bootcamp. Intern will gain tech startup experience in user outreach and integrating html/CSS into Ruby on Rails. <br><br></p>

    <p style="font-weight: bold;">Responsibilities:</p>
